Package: webglobe
Type: Package
Title: 3D Interactive Globes for R
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2017-04-18
Author: Richard Barnes
Maintainer: Richard Barnes <rbarnes@umn.edu>
NeedsCompilation: yes
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3), dplyr (>= 0.5)
Suggests: knitr, R.rsp (>= 0.41.0), rmarkdown (>= 1.0), testthat
License: MIT + file LICENCE
Authors@R: c(person("Richard", "Barnes", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "rbarnes@umn.edu"))
Description: Visualizing global data on a flat map can lead to poor interpretations due to projection distortion. This package address this problem by displaying data on an interactive 3D globe in the web browser.
URL: https://github.com/r-barnes/webglobe/
